      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "UserApi  ─登录/注册→  用户身份认证\nOrderApi ─商品校验→  ProductApi  ─库存扣减→  InOutRecordApi\nOrderApi ─积分发放→  UserPointApi  ─积分记录→  UserPointRecordApi\nOrderApi ─消息通知→  InformationApi\nProductApi ─类目校验→  CategoryApi  ─删除检查→  ProductApi",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "UserApi  ─登录/注册→  用户身份认证\nOrderApi ─商品校验→  ProductApi  ─库存扣减→  InOutRecordApi\nOrderApi ─积分发放→  UserPointApi  ─积分记录→  UserPointRecordApi\nOrderApi ─消息通知→  InformationApi\nProductApi ─类目校验→  CategoryApi  ─删除检查→  ProductApi",
      "autoResize": true,
