      "text": "跨模块接口调用关系矩阵",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "跨模块接口调用关系矩阵",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "syncedAt": "2026-05-18T08:32:52.699Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-05-18T08:32:52.694Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "dep_txt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 760,
      "width": 539.6328125,
      "height": 73.6,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#555",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b05",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2040678580,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 295723188,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779093168959,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "调用方 → 被调用方:\nOrderApi.over()      → ProductService.inOutBatch()   库存批量扣减  |  OrderApi.over()      → UserPointService.updatePoint()   积分发放\nOrderApi.over()      → InformationService.saveInformation()  消息通知  |  OrderApi.reject()     → InformationService.saveInformation()  拒绝通知\nUserPointApi.convert() → ProductService.outBatchByPoints()  积分兑换出库  |  UserSignInApi.sign() → UserPointService.updatePoint()   签到积分\nAwardApi.draw()       → UserPointService.updatePoint()   抽奖积分  |  CategoryApi.delete()  → ProductService.existByCategoryId()  类目删除校验\nProductApi.inout()    → InOutProductRecordService.addRecord() 出入库记录  |  ProductApi.add/update/delete → HistoryOperationService.log() 操作日志\nBackupApi.export()    → ProductService + CategoryService + OrderService  全量导出  |  SlideshowApi          → WxCloudStorageService  云存储管理\n模块内部CRUD: list → add/update/delete 各模块标准资源管理  |  调用方向: → 表示被调用模块, 反向依赖由@Lazy注解解除循环",
      "fontSize": 8,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "调用方 → 被调用方:\nOrderApi.over()      → ProductService.inOutBatch()   库存批量扣减  |  OrderApi.over()      → UserPointService.updatePoint()   积分发放\nOrderApi.over()      → InformationService.saveInformation()  消息通知  |  OrderApi.reject()     → InformationService.saveInformation()  拒绝通知\nUserPointApi.convert() → ProductService.outBatchByPoints()  积分兑换出库  |  UserSignInApi.sign() → UserPointService.updatePoint()   签到积分\nAwardApi.draw()       → UserPointService.updatePoint()   抽奖积分  |  CategoryApi.delete()  → ProductService.existByCategoryId()  类目删除校验\nProductApi.inout()    → InOutProductRecordService.addRecord() 出入库记录  |  ProductApi.add/update/delete → HistoryOperationService.log() 操作日志\nBackupApi.export()    → ProductService + CategoryService + OrderService  全量导出  |  SlideshowApi          → WxCloudStorageService  云存储管理\n模块内部CRUD: list → add/update/delete 各模块标准资源管理  |  调用方向: → 表示被调用模块, 反向依赖由@Lazy注解解除循环",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15,
      "syncedAt": "2026-05-18T08:32:52.699Z",
      "source": "frontend_sync",
      "syncTimestamp": "2026-05-18T08:32:52.694Z"
    },
